        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>Pro Grand 48" All-Gas</h3>
          <p class="model-list">PRG486GDH · PRG486EDG · PRG486WDG · PRG486WLG</p>
          <p>Same rangetop as the dual-fuel, gas oven and gas secondary oven. Often specified by clients with a gas line to the range but no 240V circuit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>Pro Grand 36" Dual-Fuel and Gas</h3>
          <p class="model-list">PRD366WHU · PRD366GHU · PRG366WG · PRG364WLG</p>
          <p>The 36" footprint fits tighter LA kitchen layouts — condos, second homes, remodels where a 48" won't work. Same Star Burner and ExtraLow technology.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>Pro Harmony 30"</h3>
