          <p>The compact Pro platform. Shared service parts with Pro Grand for ignition and control, smaller cavity and simpler oven architecture.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="footnote">Legacy Pro lines — PD series, older CIT rangetops paired with wall ovens — we service when parts are still available from BSH. Discontinued 1990s outdoor and wall-heater products are not in scope (see <a href="/brands/thermador/">the Thermador hub page</a>).</p>
