      <h2>If your range is under warranty, call Thermador first</h2>
      <p>Thermador's standard warranty is 2 years on major components, 1 year on everything else. Inside that window, Thermador dispatches a Factory-Certified contractor at no parts cost to you. The numbers to call are Thermador customer service at <strong>1-800-735-4328</strong> — they handle scheduling.</p>
      <p>Where we come in: after the warranty expires, or when Thermador's 5-day dispatch window doesn't fit your schedule, or when the warranty work has been done twice already and the problem is back. We're factory-trained but independent — lower labor rates, faster response, same parts.</p>
      <p>We also handle the out-of-warranty diagnostic work for customers who want a second opinion before making a repair-or-replace decision on a ten-year-old Pro Grand. A $89 diagnostic visit is a lot cheaper than a $2,400 "maybe the board" repair that doesn't fix the real problem.</p>
